riences\n|-\n|2019\n|Chakravyuh mein #SockThem\n|Divine\n|Karan Kanchan, Divine\n|[[Puma (brand)|PUMA]]\n|-\n|2019\n|Legends\n|Divine, Aditi Ramesh\n|Karan Kanchan\n|[[Red Bull BC One]]\n|}\n\n=== Playback Singer ===\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n!Year\n!Film\n!Song\n!Singer(s)\n!Producer(s)\n|-\n|2017\n|[[Rum (film)|Rum]]\n|Pori Pathi Vizhum\n|Diwakar, Divine \n|Vijaya Raghavendra\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|2018\n|''[[Mukkabaaz]]''\n|Paintra\n|Divine\n|[[Nucleya]]\n|-\n|[[Blackmail (2018 film)|Blackmail]]\n|Badla\n|[[Amit Trivedi]], Divine\n|Kiran Das\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\" |2019\n|rowspan=\"5\"|[[Gully Boy]]\n|Apna Time Aayega (as lyricist)\n|[[Ranveer Singh]]\n|Dub Sharma, Divine\n|-\n|Azadi\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Divine\n|Dub Sharma, Divine\n|-\n|Sher Aya Sher\n|Chandrashekar Kunder\n|-\n|Mere Gully Mein \n|Ranveer Singh, Divine, [[Naezy]]\n|Sez On The Beat\n|-\n|Doori (as lyricist)\n|Ranveer Singh\n|[[Rishi Rich]]\n|}\n\n== Awards and nominations ==\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n! Year !! Award !! Category !! Song !! Result !! Ref\n|-\n| 2013 || Rolling Stone India 2013 || Best Video Award || Yeh Mera Bombay || {{won}} ||\n|-\n| 2018 || Outlook Social Media Award || Musician of the Year || {{n/a}} || {{won}} || \n|-\n| 2015 || [[Global Indian Music Academy Awards|GIMA Awards]] || Best EDM Track of the Year || Jungle Raja ('''Bass Rani''') by Nucleya || {{won}} || \n|-\n| 2020 || [[65th Filmfare Awards]] || [[Filmfare Award for Best Lyricist|Best Lyrics]] || '''Apna Time Aayega''' ([[Gully Boy]]) with Ankur Tiwari || {{won}} || <ref>{{cite news |title=Kesari lyricist Manoj Muntashir vows to boycott award shows as Filmfare Best Lyrics award goes to Gully Boy |url=https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/news/kesari-lyricist-manoj-muntashir-vows-boycott-award-shows-filmfare-best-lyrics-award-goes-gully-boy-508291 |accessdate=19 February 2020 |work=PINKVILLA |language=en}}</ref>\n|}\n\n== Documentaries ==\n\n* ''Gully Life: Story of Divine.'' 2019 documentary, [[Discovery Channel (India)|Disco