est.com.mk/default.asp?id=8945&idg=1&idb=266&rubrika=Makedonija \"\u0423\u0431\u0438\u0435\u043d \u0424\u0430\u0434\u0438\u043b \u041b\u0438\u043c\u0430\u043d\u0438, \u043a\u043e\u043c\u0430\u043d\u0434\u0430\u043d\u0442 \u043d\u0430 \u0442\u0435\u0440\u043e\u0440\u0438\u0441\u0442\u0438\u0442\u0435 \u0437\u0430 \u041a\u0443\u043c\u0430\u043d\u043e\u0432\u043e\"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131002135805/http://star.vest.com.mk/default.asp?id=8945&idg=1&idb=266&rubrika=Makedonija |date=2 October 2013 }}. \u0412\u0435\u0441\u0442. 28 May 2001</ref><br /> {{flagicon image|Uck Nla logo.svg|border=|size=16px}} [[Tahir Sinani]]{{KIA}}<ref name=\"lajmpress.com\"/><br /> {{flagicon image|Uck Nla logo.svg|border=|size=16px}} [[Rahim Beqiri]]{{KIA}}<ref name=\"U\u00c7K Menaj\">[http://soros.org.mk/dokumenti/FIOOM-Poraka-i-nadez-tom-II.pdf \"U\u00c7K. Message and hope. Part II\"] by Petrit Menaj. Open Society Institute, Macedonia. Skopje. 2008</ref><br />{{flagicon image|Uck Nla logo.svg|border=|size=16px}} Hamdi Ndrecaj<br />{{flagicon image|Uck Nla logo.svg|border=|size=16px}} Gezim Ostreni <br />{{flagicon image|Uck Nla logo.svg|border=|size=16px}} Samidin Xhezairi\n| commander2  = {{flagicon|Republic of Macedonia}} [[Boris Trajkovski]]<br />{{flagicon|Republic of Macedonia}} [[Ljub\u010do Georgievski]]<br />{{flagicon|Republic of Macedonia}} [[Pande Petrovski]] <small>(from 12 June 2001) </small><br />{{flagicon|Republic of Macedonia}} [[Jovan Andrevski]] <small>(to 12 June 2001) </small><br />{{flagicon|Republic of Macedonia}} [[Ljube Bo\u0161koski]] <small>(from 15 May 2001) </small> <br />{{flagicon|Republic of Macedonia}} [[Dosta Dimovska]] <small>(to 13 May 2001)  </small><br />{{flagicon|Republic of Macedonia}} [[Vlado Bu\u010dkovski]] <small>(from 13 May 2001) </small><br />{{flagicon|Republic of Macedonia}} [[Ljuben Paunovski]] <small>(to 13 May 2001)</small>\n| strength1   = {{flagicon image|Uck Nla logo.svg|border=|size=18px}} 6,000\u20137,000\